captions.text: OH NO! SPACE LASER PONIES!! THEY'RE BACK!!!

OH CHAOS, PLEASE SAVE ME I'M SORRY I STOLE
YOUR HEART AND LEFT YOU WITHOUT SAYING GOODBYE!!
LUCY! LET'S MAKE A MOVIE!! RIGHT HUGGING NOW.
(Sigh) Did you just say hugging instead of fuc- ARGHH
Ben! Can we do this later?

Okay for this scene what I want you to do
is take this prop gun and shoot this prop old lady.
Awwww! Now shoot her in the face.
Wow, this is a really good prop.
Wait! Is this a real old lady?!
I'm not shooting an old lady!!
I WILL SHOOT YOU IN THE FACE!
Yeah, i'm still not doing this.
Beautiful. What do you think Kate?

Hey guys! So yeah, thanks for letting me murder
someone!!
You guys can't do this you're cops!
Oh, we're not cops. We're perverts... Dressed as cops.
Hey! Did you shoot that perfectly good old lady?!
(Gun shots, Alice screaming and montage music)

Ben, you are my friend, but your filmmaking
is tearing a hole in my heart.

Ben, my only friend your wild actions are
tearing us apart.

And I know it's all just for show, but you
must know I will say no and I will go...

So, Ben you're still my friend, but I will
not shoot old ladies for your art.
I'm sorry Lucy. I didn't know you felt that way.

It's fine, I just needed to let you know how
I feel. Thanks for listening.

You foiled our invasion! Now we are going
to probe you! TO DEATH!!
How did they see through my disguise?!
Hey, do you want to probe us too?
Okay! New song! I DON'T WANNA DIE!!
Hey Lucy! Could you teach me how to play guitar?
Yeah, how do you hit A minor?
Ohhhh... Yeah, you do it like this!
Wow, what a great film shoot.
